Title: Lacoste Pour Homme EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: He doesn’t care for silk ties, flashy motorbikes or the umpteenth App on the latest gadget - he’s the salt of the earth. Not one to accessorise as he follows some of the old-world masculine dictums, Lacoste Pour Homme is his only indulgence. A creation by Claude Dir, this rustic Eau De Toilette is made for the established brand of Lacoste. Opening with a top note of lush extracts of plum mixed with refreshing notes of apple, the sweet citrus of bergamot and tart notes of grapefruit. Moving into the heart of the fragrance, it merges the fragrant spice of cinnamon, sweet and spicy pink pepper, intense and resinous cardamom with the fruity spice of juniper. Descending into the base note, rich resinous labdanum along with exotic and fragrant notes of sandalwood, soothing and heavy musk, creamy vanilla, warming cedar are drizzled with sugary and heady notes of rum. This luxury fragrance bathes you in a naturally sensual aura, saluting the core values of masculinity. A sleek rectangular bottle, it glistens a hue of steel grey and also features a textured stopper. Made of crystal-clear glass, the bottle gleams on top of your dresser. A whiff of Lacoste Pour Homme and he embraces the raw spirit that makes him truly unique.

Title: Dunhill Desire Red EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: A perfect fit for the hustle and bustle of the regular day in a man’s life, this EDT from Dunhill is what you’ve always been looking for. Woody-Oriental Composition An exotic overshadow of the classic woody is here with Dunhill Desire Red for the masculine undertone for every one of your days and activities. Sophisticated and Playful Aroma That playful swank with a serious shadow exudes this Desire as it mixes the much loved masculine notes with a tease to leave your lady floored. Blend of Warm and Sensual Fruits & Wood, Low Notes of Vanilla and Musk  You couldn't go closer to perfect; acclaimed perfumer Michel Almairac blends notes that have won hearts and senses for centuries with the Dunhill game to bring to you the amalgamation of a warm and intense scent to wear. Ruby-red glass - Attractive and Modern Design The upgraded design of the bottle ensures you always have utmost comfort while spraying the scent on because of the friendly and modern build.

Title: Fashion Police Pure Gold EDP  -  100 ml(For Women)
Ferrari Black EDT  -  125 ml(For Men)
Description: In a cozy kitchenette, he cooks up a scrumptious fare for the one he cares for; he is the epitome of the quintessential nice guy and does everything by the book. His charm is natural as is his warm smile but make no mistake, dynamic power lurks just beneath the surface. Ferrari presents him with an ode in the form of Black, a luxury Eau de Toilette that is almost second nature to him. With a sillage that extends long after he has left the room, his memories last even when his presence does not. The opening accents of this aromatic fougere are lime, plum, bergamot and crunchy, red apple that remind you of rich, full orchards in the heights of summer. It gradually melts into the luscious, rich heart notes of cinnamon, jasmine and velvety rose with just a tinge of spicy cinnamon. Time wears on and amber, musk and cedar make an appearance to ground the fragrance and wrap it all up in a cozy vanilla base. This scent is captured in a classic, black bottle which is resplendent with all the glory of brand Ferrari, right down to the prancing horse. For the man who revels in the glory of it all, this alluring scent is but an adornment.

Title: Adidas Ice Dive with Offer EDT  -  100 ml(For Men)
Description: Perfect for waking yourself up to a great morning and a solid start to the day, Ice Dive from Adidas is a fragrance that imparts unbeatable freshness to your senses. Fresh Ozonic Fragrance, Long Lasting With ozonic components, the Eau de Toilette is almost clinically fresh, a fail-safe way to ensure that you smell nice all day long. Ergonomic Shape The flacon that comprises of the fragrance is one that is designed to fit the palm of your hand well for you to properly dispense off the perfume. Title: Hugo XX EDT  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Fruity and floral, XX from the house of Hugo Boss embodies the essence of the modern woman and her spirit of confluence through divergence. Total harmony between the masculine and the feminine is over-rated and outmoded; XX is emblematic of a new generation with a unique take on relationships. With its underlying tones of sensuality and sophistication, Hugo XX defines the aura of a mature woman - audacious yet alluring. The gourmand and fruity notes of this Eau de Toilette open with a delightful top note of lychee, blackcurrant and mandarin, only to unite with a soothing heart note of basmati rice and jasmine sambac to create a contemporary and intriguing aroma. The musky scent of sandalwood in the base note leaves behind a trail of luxuriously earthy essence which provides a beguiling contrast to the top and heart notes - just like the inherent contradiction between sexes, between the yin and the yang. Yet the accords unite and synchronize in a manner that is reminiscent of the essential attraction and aggression between each of these incongruent denominations. The seductively intense Hugo XX is encased in cylindrical vials with shiny golden tones, inspired by bottles of colourful spray-paint. Unpretentious and vibrant, XX defines the spirit of modern femininity.

Title: Escada Absolutely Me EDP  -  75 ml(For Women)
Description: Intensely addictive and ultimately tender, a single whiff of Absolutely Me leads you down the path of olfactory nirvana. From the celebrated house of Escada, the fragrance is an incredible sumptuous blend of the most succulent and mouth watering elements that leaves your senses begging for more. The luxury scent symbolises the raw desirability of a woman, alluring and spontaneous. The Eau de Parfum draws you into its alluring depths leaving you lost in the luscious depths making you beg for more of its intense freshness. She is a woman of today who walks barefoot, prefers sweatshirts and old shorts to haute couture and eats ice cream straight out of the carton and still manages to look beautifully perfect and Escada honors her need to be just herself and embrace all that she is. All three layers of the fragrance are extremely delicious to the point where you start giving in to your cravings and indulge yourself. Creamy opening notes with accords of fresh, red raspberries, soft red rose and spicy pink peppercorns remind you of rich, creamy desserts denied in favor of figure. The heart notes are lavishly scrumptious with the accords of jasmine and wild hawthorn. Smooth and saucy, rose macaron adds its divine flavor to the melee. Absolutely Me closes with musky accords and edible texture of vanilla which gives the dry down a very creamy sensuality. Escada Absolutely Me is presented in a flacon that draws inspiration from the symbol of infinity which signifies the undeniable draw of the woman it adorns. Let the smooth warmth of Absolutely Me wash over you as you assert your independence and sensuality.

Title: Ralph Lauren Polo Supreme Oud Eau de Parfum  -  125 ml(For Boys)

It is developed by perfumer Carlos Benaim. The fragrance offers quality, strength and longevity.The oriental - woody composition begins with spicy accords of pink pepper and cinnamon. The heart features smoky accord of Indian oud, laid on the base of vetiver and guaiac wood.It is available in black bottle and box, with gold lettering, as 125 ml Eau de Parfum.
